            "title": "Direitos Humanos, g\u00eanero, cidadania e educa\u00e7\u00e3o",
            "abstract": [
                "Ao longo desses vinte e quatro anos de atividades em Mar\u00edlia e regi\u00e3o, no \u00e2mbito acad\u00eamico, o NUDHUC tem se dedicado \u00e0 forma\u00e7\u00e3o, \u00e0 produ\u00e7\u00e3o de publica\u00e7\u00f5es e \u00e0 orienta\u00e7\u00e3o de pesquisas, pretendendo promover reflex\u00e3o cr\u00edtica e aprofundar o conhecimento acerca da educa\u00e7\u00e3o em direitos humanos, g\u00eanero, ra\u00e7a/etnia, cidadania, dentre outros temas. Ap\u00f3s a realiza\u00e7\u00e3o dos eventos cient\u00edficos, visando sempre relembrar a hist\u00f3ria de luta para garantia dos direitos de todas as pessoas na Hist\u00f3ria do nosso pa\u00eds e da humanidade, para que as novas gera\u00e7\u00f5es a conhe\u00e7am e reflitam sobre o valor da liberdade, dos direitos humanos, do respeito e da dignidade para todas as pessoas, valores estes da Democracia, tem sido publicados textos originados dos eventos. Nessa perspectiva, contamos, nesta colet\u00e2nea, com a participa\u00e7\u00e3o de pesquisadores(as) e militantes defensores dos Direitos Humanos da Argentina, da Espanha e do Brasil que t\u00eam se dedicado a registrar a Hist\u00f3ria, analisando, do ponto de vista geral, atrav\u00e9s da Sociologia, da Psicologia e da Educa\u00e7\u00e3o, os condicionantes para os avan\u00e7os e recuos no que diz respeito \u00e0 garantia dos Direitos Humanos, para pensarmos nos desafios da atualidade que est\u00e3o postos num momento em que constatamos a\u00e7\u00f5es de grupos conservadores se organizando pela aprova\u00e7\u00e3o de projetos como o Escola sem Partido, al\u00e9m de ataques aos direitos humanos e seus defensores e defensoras, que mostram a resist\u00eancia dando exemplo de exerc\u00edcio da cidadania plena",
                "Over these twenty-four years of activities in Mar\u00edlia and region, in the academic field, NUDHUC has been dedicated to training, production of publications and guidance of research, intending to promote critical reflection and deepen knowledge about education in human rights , gender, race/ethnicity, citizenship, among other topics. After holding the scientific events, always aiming to remember the history of the struggle to guarantee the rights of all people in the history of our country and of humanity, so that the new generations get to know it and reflect on the value of freedom, human rights, of respect and dignity for all people, values of Democracy, texts originating from the events have been published. In this perspective, in this collection, we have the participation of researchers and activists defending Human Rights from Argentina, Spain and Brazil who have dedicated themselves to recording History, analyzing, from a general point of view, through Sociology , Psychology and Education, the conditions for advances and setbacks with regard to the guarantee of Human Rights, to think about the current challenges that are posed at a time when we see actions by conservative groups organizing themselves for the approval of projects such as the School without a Party, in addition to attacks on human rights and their defenders, who show resistance by giving an example of exercising full citizenship"
            ],
